ed based on a hidden 'sanity' meter not visible in the UI. Pierrot's route contains the most aggressive pruning — removing options that would lead to early endings.\"}]\n11:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\",\"children\":\"64 Red Threads Connected\"}]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"href\":\"/theories/pierrot-remembers-routes\",\"className\":\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\",\"children\":\"Read Full Investigation →\"}]\n13:[\"$\",\"div\",\"114-C\",{\"className\":\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\",\"children\":[\"File No: \",\"114-C\"]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-3\",\"children\":\"Theory: Why Does the Mirror Hall Remember Previous Routes?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\",\"children\":\"The Mirror Hall's layout changes between playthroughs, showing rooms from routes the player has not yet completed. The broken mirror widens after 3 routes, showing a reflection of the player's desktop.\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-surface border border-outline/10 p-2 mb-3\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\",\"children\":[\"SPOILER: \",\"The mirror is actually a camera.\"]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"href\":\"/lore/mirror-hall\",\"className\":\"text-primary font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase hover:underline\",\"children\":\"Read Full Investigation →\"}]]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",\"001-Z\",{\"className\":\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"fon