-Researched Lore Archive\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\",\"children\":\"Inside This Archive — What the community has built over two years of testing and documentation\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\",\"children\":\"Character Relationship Analysis\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\",\"children\":\"How Pierrot, Harlequin, The Doctor, and Columbina interconnect across routes. Cross-route dialogue changes and shared memory triggers.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\",\"children\":\"Ending Requirement Documentation\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\",\"children\":\"Verified unlock conditions for 8+ endings. Scene-by-scene requirements, replay dependencies, and hidden trigger documentation.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\",\"children\":\"Route-Specific Walkthroughs\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\",\"children\":\"Step-by-step guides for Pierrot's silent route, Harlequin's fractured route, The Doctor's memory ro